94
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,520
<i>You must serve me too, Earth.</i>

95
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,400
<i>Why?</i>

96
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:36,039
<i>Because you said
you serve anything that's cute.</i>

97
