Was it that bad?

131
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,320
Some human schoolers at S-Tar almost died.

132
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:49,040
Seriously?

133
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:51,640
The only way to break the curse
is to leave the club.

134
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,000
I'm going to use this.

135
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,720
Almost died?

136
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:13,480
We have lots of clubs in school.

137
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:16,840
I don't highly recommend them though.
They're mostly boring.

138
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:18,440
