170
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:04,720
Just help me. Stop complaining.

171
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,600
Mawin! Be careful.

172
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,200
{\an8}Yes, Miss Luna.

173
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,240
Always ordering me around.

174
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:16,240
ANNUAL SCHOOL CLUB FAIR
S-TAR SCHOOL

175
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:22,000
Hello, everyone.

176
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:24,040
