178
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:28,600
After being canceled for five years,

179
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:32,040
today, our Astronomy Club is back.

180
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,760
What?

181
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,960
What the heck?

182
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,120
Join us for an outer space adventure

183
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:42,640
by meeting in the club room
behind the basketball court.

184
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:44,760
