is still less than four.

259
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:45,640
We must find one more member
within the next week.

260
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:49,200
Do you know anyone
who might be interested in joining?

261
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,960
